
Ranger Help for: check
======================

SYNTAX:      check <weapon>/check <weapon1> against <weapon2>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     25 sp
SKILL TYPE:  knowledge

SUMMARY:    
This skills lets a Ranger check how good a weapon is. It will show various
ratings on certain aspects of the weapon. You can also check a weapon
against another weapon, in which case it will show information for both
weapons and then give you an idea of which one might be better.

